
## **Company Overview**

Play or Pay is a social gaming platform.
We bring people together through fun, interactive games.
You play with real people, in real time.

You can **create a game** or **join one instantly**.
No complicated setup. No pressure. Just interaction.

---

## **Games & Gameplay**

Players can create their own games or join existing ones.

When creating a game, you choose:

* The game type
* Whether it’s **public** or **private**

**Public games** appear in the lobby.
Anyone can see them. Anyone can join.

**Private games** come with a shareable link.
Copy it. Send it to friends. Keep it exclusive.

Each game happens in its own space.
Only invited or joined players can participate.
No outsiders. No interruptions.

---

## **Token Economy**

Tokens power the platform.
They represent real value.

* **1 token equals 1 shilling**
* Tokens move **between players**, not from the company

You earn tokens by being engaging, fun, and worth playing with.
Other players choose to credit you during games.

This keeps interactions lively.
It rewards effort, creativity, and presence.

You always see your token balance.
Nothing hidden. No guesswork.

---

## **Pricing, Earnings & Withdrawals**

Joining games is **free**.
Playing is always optional.

Tokens are used to enhance the experience.
They act as incentives, not requirements.

When you withdraw:

* The platform takes a **20% service fee**
* The rest is yours

This helps us:

* Maintain the platform
* Improve performance
* Keep everything running smoothly

Withdrawals are processed within **48 hours**.
Funds are sent to the mobile number you provide.

Simple. Transparent. Reliable.

---

## **Accounts & Onboarding**

Creating an account is free.
The signup process is fast and straightforward.

You control your profile.
You can update your details at any time.

You can also delete your account directly from your profile page.
No emails. No delays.

Due to platform capacity and safety standards,
account registrations may be limited as the community grows.

---

## **Safety & Community Guidelines**

Play or Pay is built on respect.

We promote:

* Friendly interactions
* Mutual respect
* Healthy conversations

We strictly prohibit:

* Bullying or harassment
* Sale or promotion of drugs or substances
* Any harmful or abusive behavior

Violations lead to account action.
Sometimes immediately.

Everyone deserves a safe space to interact.

